<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When calling</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
zf enable layout
</code></pre>

<p>It adds the wrong ini code:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
resources.layout.layoutPath = "APPLICATION_PATH \"layouts/scripts\""
</code></pre>

<p>Should be:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
resources.layout.layoutPath = APPLICATION_PATH "/layouts/scripts"
</code></pre>

